title: McDonough School's Quinn: Relation of Trade to Election (Audio)
itunes:title: McDonough School's Quinn: Relation of Trade to Election (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Dennis Quinn, Professor of International Political Economy at Georgetown University’s McDonough School of Business, on new study: “Winners and Losers in International Trade: Effects on U.S. Presidential Voting."
